  - `form/exhibit/_internal/ExhibitFrame.tsx` 新增导出 `EXHIBIT_FRAME_WIDTH_CARD = 355` / `EXHIBIT_FRAME_WIDTH_FLUSH = 375` 两个常量；ExhibitFrame 外层改为 `width: ${card ? 355 : 375}px + flexShrink: 0 + boxSizing: border-box`，按 card prop 切换固定宽度
  - 5 个非 ExhibitFrame 包裹的 cell（ExhibitVeriFace / ExhibitAmountListTitleExternal / ExhibitAggregateMultiFold / ExhibitInformationList / ExhibitInformationListPlainText / ExhibitInformationListAmount）均统一引用上述两个常量：
    - 固定 card 三件（VeriFace / AmountListTitleExternal / AggregateMultiFold）→ 固定 355
    - 三件 InformationList → 按 card prop 在 355 / 375 之间切换
  - 全部 cell 外层补 `flexShrink: 0 + boxSizing: border-box`，避免在 flex 父容器中被收缩
  - parts/* 内部嵌套原子（GroupTitleH1 / SubCellFlush / SubListFlush / FoldingPureHeader / CellAmountTag / AmountList / SubInnercard / CollapseNestAmount / AmountNestList）保持 `width: 100%`，作为 cell 内部填充其父固定宽容器（无需感知 355 / 375）
